{
  "stem": "19690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 66.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in one way, he was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very hesitant in that he never saw the danger that was coming, and always negated it as being, oh, nothing to worry about.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even when others were leaving, he insisted there was nothing to be worried about until nearly the very end, when it was too late.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother was an excellent cook.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was a tremendous disciplinarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Her most famous saying was, any [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Ohrfeigen that she missed were wasted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she would hit me at the least provocation when I did something wrong, whereas my father would always say, let the kid go, let the kid go.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so my mother was a disciplinarian and very strict with me, and a very smart woman in many, many ways, because at a very early age, she taught me things that would come handy much later on.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember when I was six or seven years old, she taught me how to mend socks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She insisted that I knew the birth dates of all the relatives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When I was about eight, she started having me memorize addresses, knowing what was coming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all these things were then in my head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And no matter what I lost, it wasn't until I got to Switzerland many years later that I wrote all these things down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were still as fluent as that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as a result, I was able to get a hold of relatives and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She did most of the cooking for our household.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When I was little-- when I was born, we lived in a house separate from my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a house that my grandparents owned.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
